INSTRUCTIONS FOR GOOGLE CLOUD, AMAZON CLOUD, VERIZON CLOUD, CTS CLOUD, CTS HYBRID CLOUD

SERVER REQUIRMENTS FOR FUSION PRO VERSION3.0

01) SERVER OR VIRTUAL SERVER RUNNING WINDOWS SERVER 2016 or 2019.
02) FULLY PATCHED TO CURRENT.
03) DOTNET 3.5, 4.5, and 4.8 INSTALLED
04) IIS SERVER 10 WITH PHP 7.4 FROM WEB PLATFORM INSTALLER WITH DEDICATED IP FROM PROVIDER
05) SQL SERVER EXPRESS 2016 WITH REPLICATION OR LATER VERSIONS (IE FULL SQL VERSIONS OK TOO)
06) ALL PREREQUISTES FOR SHAREPOINT SERVER 2016 (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/sharepoint/install/install-sharepoint-server-2016-on-one-server)
07) SHAREPOINT 2016 INSTALLED
08) FUSION SHELL 1.0 INSTALLED FROM GITHUB
09) ADOBE COLDFUSION SERVER 2018 OR LATER INSTALLED AND INTEGRATED WITH THE WEB SERVER
10) PHP MANAGER INSTALLED ON IIS
11) ALL AUTHENTICATION METHODS INSTALLED IN IIS
12) AT LEAST 4GB OF RAM FOR THE WINDOW SERVER
13) THE FOLLOWING DOMAINS PROVISIONED (PEM.DOMAIN.X, GEM.DOMAIN.X, CONFIGURATION.DOMAIN.X, SEM.DOMAIN.X)
14) CERTBOT, AND WIN-ACME INSTALLED TO C:\INETPUB\WINACME\

15) G/A RECOMMEND THE FOLLOWING GENERAL PURPOSE FILE STRUCTURE FOR OUR COMBINEDTOOLSET SO CREATE THESE DIRECTORIES FIRST:
a) C:\WEB\GREENVILLE\DOMAIN.XXX      AS WEB ROOT DIRECTORY
b) C:\WEBLOGS\GREENVILLE\DOMAIN.XXX  AS LOG DIRECTORY
c) C:\WEBCERTS\GREENVILLE\DOMAIN.XXX AS SSL DIRECTORY
d) c:\WEB\GREENVILLE\SHAREPOINT2016
e) c:\WEB\GREENVILLE\SQLSERVER2016
f) c:\WEB\GREENVILLE\ADOBECOLDFUSION2018
g) C:\WEB\GREENVILLE\OPENSOURCE\JOOMLA
h) C:\WEB\GREENVILLE\OPENSOURCE\WORDPRESS
i) C:\WEB\GREENVILLE\OPENSOURCE\DRUPAL
j) C:\WEB\GREENVILLE\OPENSOURCE\TOMATOCART
(THIS INSTALL WILL TAKE SERVERAL DAYS IF YOU HAVENT DONE IT BEFORE).
